FBIS4-36079 "drnes109_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 ISRAEL Rocket, Artillery Duels Continue in South Rocket, Artillery Duels Continue in South Rockets Fired on Town, SLA Post NC0706101494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 0930 GMT 7 Jun 94 NC0706101494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] Our military correspondent reports that a South Lebanese Army [SLA] post in Kawkaba came under terrorist machine-gun and RPG fire today. This was followed by artillery and rocket bombardment of the same post from terrorist positions in Qilya, Yuhmur, Maydun, and 'Ayn al-Tinah. There were no casualties. The SLA returned the fire with the appropriate weapons. Our correspondent adds that the terrorists then fired rockets on Marj 'Uyun area from their positions in Mashgharah and 'Ayn al- Tinah. SLA and Israeli artillery are returning the fire.
